high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the small, black table in the corner.
Pick up the apple that is on the black table between the sponge and the salt.
Turn to your right and walk across the room to the stove.
Place the apple in the microwave, heat it up, then remove it from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk back to the small, black table in the corner.
Put the apple on the small, black table, to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the small black table next to the white table.
Pick the apple up from the table.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the microwave above the stove.
Put the apple in the microwave and turn it on and then open the door and take the apple out and shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room and turn right to stand in front of the small black table.
Put the apple on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the small black table.
Pick up the apple on the table.
Turn around, bring the apple to the left, to the microwave over the stove.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Bring the heated apple back across the room to the small black table on the right.
Put the heated apple on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black table.
Pick the apple up off of the table.
Turn around and walk to the microwave above the store.
Open the microwave, heat the apple, and then take it out of the microwave again.
Turn around and head back to the black table.
Place the apple back on the table to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on a black table.

high_descs: Turn right towards the small black table.
Pick up the apple from the table.
Turn around towards the round table and make a left towards the oven.
Heat the apple in the microwave and take out the apple.
Turn around towards the small black table on the right.
Place the apple to the right of the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the apple from the black table.

high_descs: Turn right and approach the small dark side table
Pick up the red apple from the table
Turn around and walk over to the microwave
Place the apple into the microwave and cook it
Turn around and walk back to the small dark side table
Place the apple down on the side table
anns.task_desc: Cook the apple in the microwave
